OL,3,CThree men jailed for violent disorder
OL,4,Cfollowing Southport stabbings
OL,6,FThree men have been jailed for their
OL,7,Fpart in disturbances which followed
OL,8,Fthe deaths of three young girls in
OL,9,FSouthport.
OL,11,FThe court heard a 38 year old man from
OL,12,FSouthport threw missiles, including a
OL,13,Fbrick at police, while a second man of
OL,14,Fthe same age, damaged a police car.
OL,16,FThe judge at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,17,Fsaid those involved in the violence
OL,18,Fhad to accept responsibility for the
OL,19,Fimpact on their community and the
OL,20,Fnation.
