OL,3,CThree men jailed for violent disorder
OL,4,Cfollowing Southport stabbings
OL,6,FThe men were jailed for a combined
OL,7,Fseven years and eight months for their
OL,8,Frole in violent disorder in Southport,
OL,9,Fthe night after the stabbing at a
OL,10,Fdance class and in Liverpool city
OL,11,Fcentre on Saturday 3 August.
OL,13,FPhilip Prescott, 38, of Sefton Street,
OL,14,FSouthport, was sentenced to two years
OL,15,Fand four months after pleading guilty
OL,16,Fto violent disorder in Southport.
OL,18,FHe was part of a crowd who gathered at
OL,19,Fthe corner of Sussex Road and Zetland
OL,20,FStreet, in Southport, and took part in
OL,21,Fviolence aimed at officers.
