OL,3,CThree men jailed for violent disorder
OL,4,Cfollowing Southport stabbings
OL,6,FPrescott threw missiles at officers,
OL,7,Fincluding a brick from a damaged
OL,8,Fgarden wall. He was arrested six days
OL,9,Flater after local policing officers
OL,10,Fsaw him on Lord Street and recognised
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,FDavid Frank Hill, 38, of Bianca
OL,14,FStreet, Bootle, has 71 previous
OL,15,Fconvictions, pleaded guilty to violent
OL,16,Fdisorder on William Brown Street in
OL,17,FLiverpool, four days later.
OL,19,FHe was sentenced to two years after
OL,20,Fpleading guilty to violent disorder in
OL,21,FLiverpool city centre.
