OL,3,CThree men jailed for violent disorder
OL,4,Cfollowing Southport stabbings
OL,6,FHill was involved in the appalling
OL,7,Fscenes in Liverpool city centre on
OL,8,FSaturday 3 August.
OL,10,FCCTV inquiries identified him damaging
OL,11,Fa police car and taking part in
OL,12,Fdisorder on William Brown Street.
OL,14,FGareth Metcalfe, 44, of Cambridge
OL,15,FGardens, Southport was sentenced to
OL,16,Fthree years and four months after
OL,17,Fpleading guilty to violent disorder in
OL,18,FSouthport.
