OL,3,CThree men jailed for violent disorder
OL,4,Cfollowing Southport stabbings
OL,6,FMetcalfe, who also took part in the
OL,7,FSouthport disorder, was identified
OL,8,Fafter officers saw him after reviewing
OL,9,Fsocial media footage. He was arrested
OL,10,Fonly four days after the incident.
OL,12,FThe 44 year old, who the judge said
OL,13,Fhad 'entrenched racist attitude
OL,14,Ftowards muslims', was said to be front
OL,15,Fand centre of the crowd, charging at
OL,16,Fpolice.
