OL,3,CThree men jailed for violent disorder
OL,4,Cfollowing Southport stabbings
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Paul White
OL,7,Fsaid: "There are now 11 people in
OL,8,Fprison following disorder in
OL,9,FMerseyside and this number is only
OL,10,Fgoing to increase in the days and
OL,11,Fweeks ahead.
OL,13,F"It's pleasing to see the courts take
OL,14,Fviolent disorder so seriously. The
OL,15,Fincidents we saw in Southport and
OL,16,FLiverpool were appalling and not only
OL,17,Finjured multiple officers, but also
OL,18,Fcaused fear in our communities.
